# ArrangedHttpMessageHandler.Remove method

Removes a handler, identified by *identifier*.

```csharp
public bool Remove(string identifier)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| identifier | A handler identifier. |

## Return Value

true if the element is successfully found and removed; otherwise, false. This method returns false if no handler was previously registered for the *identifier*.
